{"type": "article", "id": 3432, "title": "可作咖啡桌的收纳盒", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-11T07:27:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232810NeotKiSVY9wpjJ7u.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t新加坡设计工作室 Juju 设计的这款收纳盒（也可作咖啡桌），曾亮相于米兰设计周的卫星展（  SaloneSatellite ）。设计团队将这一系列的盒子进行分类，提供 Stacking Drums 与 Big Drum 两种不同的尺寸，Stacking Drums 较为轻便小巧，内部的肋状结构不仅祈祷加固收纳盒的作用，还可以提供分类功能，使得用户更易于收纳零散小物，而 Big Drum 除了提供收纳功能之外，还可以作为咖啡桌使用。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232807n1hC4xaowk3vNcbL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.659375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232808El75kHWDCcSrz1IQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.659375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232808BtFzfKRw9DjmrA6J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052328095wylPjqXuaxZSM3Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}